  "keyFeatures": [
    "Secure, immutable Linux OS designed for Kubernetes",
    "API-driven management with no SSH or shell access",
    "Atomic updates and configuration management",
    "Multi-platform support (bare metal, cloud providers, containers)",
    "Built-in etcd for control plane nodes",
    "Comprehensive gRPC API for all system operations",
    "talosctl CLI for cluster lifecycle management",
    "Image builder and provisioning tools"
